title: Narration
---
Narrator: Today was your second day. After a brief check in with the supervisor, your second day shift is about to begin. You kept thinking about your old friend who came yesterday. It made you sleep easier last night. She still remembers you and went out of the way just to see you. You wonder if she’s gonna see you today again, you still have a lot to tell her. 
-> (The Officer told me that today, we have a special offer for our first customer. It’s one free Nasi Kunyit promo, an item to strengthen immunity but also fulfilling. I wonder who’s the lucky few.)
<<customer_leave>>
