title: Robot
---
<<declare $correctDish = false>>
OW: Excuse me sir, can I order for one wedang sereh?
-> ..uhh?
OW: Yes, I am a machine, a revolutionary finding before, and now it’s just an office worker.
OW: Is that weird for you?
-> Ah no, this is my first time seeing a robot.
    -> I’m curious, what do you need a wedang sereh for?
OW: My coworker had a stressful day, she got rejected by her crush.
-> Ouch.
OW: I want to help her to feel better.
-> Then let me help your colleague with that. Please wait for a while.
<<jump WaitForDishTiger>>
